032/**
033 * Represents an <c>HTTP 304 Not Modified</c> response.
034 *
035 * <p>
036 * Indicates that the resource has not been modified since the version specified by the request headers If-Modified-Since or If-None-Match.
037 * In such case, there is no need to retransmit the resource since the client still has a previously-downloaded copy.
038 *
039 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
040 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/JuneauRestCommonBasics">juneau-rest-common Basics</a>
041 * </ul>
042 */
043@Response
044@StatusCode(STATUS_CODE)
045@Schema(description=REASON_PHRASE)
046@FluentSetters
047public class NotModified extends BasicHttpResponse {
048
049   /** HTTP status code */
050   public static final int STATUS_CODE = 304;
051
052   /** Reason phrase */
053   public static final String REASON_PHRASE = "Not Modified";
054
055   /** Default status line */
056   private static final BasicStatusLine STATUS_LINE = BasicStatusLine.create(STATUS_CODE, REASON_PHRASE);
057
058   /** Default unmodifiable instance */
059   public static final NotModified INSTANCE = new NotModified().setUnmodifiable();
060
061   /**
062    * Constructor.
063    */
064   public NotModified() {
065      super(STATUS_LINE);
066   }
067
068   /**
069    * Copy constructor.
070    *
071    * @param copyFrom The bean to copy from.
072    */
073   public NotModified(NotModified copyFrom) {
074      super(copyFrom);
075   }
076
077   /**
078    * Constructor.
079    *
080    * <p>
081    * This is the constructor used when parsing an HTTP response.
082    *
083    * @param response The HTTP response to copy from.  Must not be <jk>null</jk>.
084    * @throws AssertionError If HTTP response status code does not match what was expected.
085    */
086   public NotModified(HttpResponse response) {
087      super(response);
088      assertStatusCode(response);
089   }
090
091   /**
092    * Creates a builder for this class initialized with the contents of this bean.
093    *
094    * @return A new builder bean.
095    */
096   public NotModified copy() {
097      return new NotModified(this);
098   }
